# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
node_modules-*/
dist-*
!dist-kabegame/
dist-kabegame/*
!dist-kabegame/.gitkeep
*.local

/release
/build

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store

# kabegame 的 tauri config 是动态生成的
# src-tauri/*/tauri.conf.json

# Tauri
target
# 隔离构建 target（target-22：22.04 VM 低 glibc；target-web：docker web-release）
target-*/
# 由 handlebars 生成
src-tauri/kabegame/capabilities/main.json
src-tauri/kabegame/tauri.conf.json
# apps/kabegame/index.html 由 handlebars 生成（见 index.html.handlebars）
apps/kabegame/index.html
src-tauri/*/gen/schemas/*
# 插件 permissions 下的 schema.json 由 tauri_plugin::Builder 在 cargo build 时生成
src-tauri-plugins/**/permissions/schemas/schema.json
src-tauri/kabegame/resources/bin/*
# 预置爬虫插件，由 crawler-plugins:package-to-resources 构建期生成，
# init_kgpg_plugin() 启动时移动进用户插件目录（见 PluginManager::seed_bundled_plugins）
src-tauri/kabegame/resources/plugins/
# Windows CEF runtime,由 os-plugin collectWindowsCefRuntime() 构建期生成
src-tauri/kabegame/resources/cef/
# macOS gen/CEFExample.app\Kabegame.app
/gen/

# bin/{platform}/ runtime libs:
# - bin/windows/ keeps the predefined DLLs in git (dokan2/libwinpthread/libva/...);
#   FFmpeg/x264 DLLs collected by os-plugin from third/FFmpeg-build/install/bin + MSYS2 are ignored.
# - bin/linux/ and bin/macos/ are fully generated by os-plugin at build time.
# - bin/android/ is gitignored, NOT committed: self-built rusty_v8 android artifacts
#   (librusty_v8_*.a + src_binding_*.rs) reproduced by `bun run build:v8` and injected via
#   RUSTY_V8_ARCHIVE / RUSTY_V8_SRC_BINDING_PATH by mode-plugin prepareEnv in android mode.
#   Do NOT put them under bin/linux/ — that dir is wiped and shipped into the deb.
/bin/windows/av*.dll
/bin/windows/swscale-*.dll
/bin/windows/swresample-*.dll
/bin/windows/libx264-*.dll
/bin/linux/
/bin/macos/
/bin/android/

# development data
/.kabegame/debug

# .cursor/

# /test/

# 外树构建目录
third/FFmpeg-build
third/x264-build
third/FFmpeg-build-*/
third/x264-build-*/

# 一些临时文件
/ignore
tmp/
.tmp/

# 临时忽略 kamechan emotion 图片资源
apps/kabegame/public/kamechan/emotion*/**/*.png

# Astro docs
apps/docs/dist
apps/docs/.astro

__pycache__/
